opsy results are important.","dimension":3,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.043771,0.085027,0.10031,0.10257,0.097716,0.090505,0.08833,0.084523,0.081146,0.08527,0.072254,0.068578],"unified_progress":[0.050151,0.076859,0.086875,0.097408,0.098325,0.093587,0.095077,0.090844,0.086908,0.088449,0.074254,0.061263]},{"section":9,"text":"The cytology shows atypical epithelial cells with features compatible with primary breast cancer.","dimension":5,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.047212,0.091601,0.096919,0.097689,0.095179,0.09459,0.091599,0.08754,0.086479,0.076888,0.069554,0.06475],"unified_progress":[0.046568,0.079666,0.091769,0.10215,0.10171,0.099586,0.096903,0.091083,0.088063,0.076599,0.067359,0.058545]},{"section":10,"text":"The comparison with her previous lung cancer cells shows differences: the breast tumor cells have a different appearance (less irregular nuclei, different chromatin) compared to the lung cancer cells.","dimension":5,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.048439,0.093543,0.097605,0.097677,0.095225,0.095636,0.092369,0.088256,0.088047,0.076365,0.067551,0.059288],"unified_progress":[0.048941,0.081703,0.093187,0.10053,0.10414,0.10182,0.098509,0.091919,0.089503,0.075153,0.063301,0.051294]},{"section":11,"text":"That suggests it's a primary breast cancer rather than a metastasis from the lung.","dimension":5,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.040718,0.080416,0.090742,0.095695,0.095068,0.094818,0.09285,0.088441,0.090889,0.082856,0.073472,0.074034],"unified_progress":[0.045938,0.071183,0.084528,0.094696,0.098179,0.097152,0.095769,0.092145,0.092348,0.08215,0.075278,0.070634]},{"section":12,"text":"Also, the histopathology from the lumpectomy of her first breast cancer shows invasive ductal carcinoma adjacent to ductal carcinoma in situ, which is typical for breast cancer.","dimension":5,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.041344,0.082747,0.090968,0.096305,0.096022,0.097544,0.094979,0.089796,0.093486,0.0805,0.070962,0.065346],"unified_progress":[0.04423,0.072016,0.089133,0.10079,0.10481,0.10354,0.099808,0.09374,0.092796,0.077496,0.0656,0.056042]},{"section":13,"text":"The new tumor's features align with primary breast cancer, and the fact that it's in the opposite breast (right vs. left previously) makes metastasis from lung less likely.","dimension":5,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.037268,0.078139,0.088533,0.094676,0.095247,0.097737,0.095391,0.090884,0.095586,0.083785,0.074213,0.068543],"unified_progress":[0.045637,0.076363,0.089305,0.098541,0.10311,0.099667,0.097729,0.0929,0.092269,0.077907,0.067168,0.059401]},{"section":14,"text":"Plus, the patient's family history doesn't mention breast cancer, but she's had two primary cancers before.","dimension":11,"group":5,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.036909,0.073295,0.08124,0.08707,0.093602,0.10541,0.097312,0.097419,0.092718,0.092928,0.078965,0.063136],"unified_progress":[0.09088,0.12396,0.10173,0.092503,0.086838,0.085274,0.080691,0.085329,0.075659,0.068995,0.059797,0.04835]},{"section":15,"text":"Other possibilities like metastasis from lung or other cancers were considered, but the cytology and histology argue against that.","dimension":5,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.029426,0.065789,0.080876,0.088708,0.092116,0.093805,0.096734,0.094256,0.1001,0.093212,0.086309,0.078668],"unified_progress":[0.040675,0.074842,0.088083,0.09768,0.099735,0.09569,0.096134,0.090622,0.091985,0.085278,0.075293,0.063984]},{"section":16,"text":"The cells don't match her previous lung cancer, so it's more likely a new primary breast cancer.","dimension":5,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.032364,0.066785,0.07755,0.084619,0.088105,0.091994,0.093626,0.092944,0.097331,0.091825,0.08802,0.094837],"unified_progress":[0.041879,0.065805,0.077448,0.087502,0.091049,0.09215,0.092002,0.09167,0.093293,0.087611,0.088446,0.091143]},{"section":17,"text":"Since she 